<%= render 'shared/mailers/header.text', title: "W9 Form Has Expired" %>

Dear <%= @vendor.business_name %>,

<%= render 'shared/mailers/status_box.text', status: :error, title: "Immediate Action Required", message: "Your W9 form has expired. We are unable to process any payments until you submit an updated form." %>

To resume payment processing for voucher transactions, please submit an updated W9 form as soon as possible.

HOW TO SUBMIT YOUR UPDATED W9:
1. Download the current W9 form from the IRS website: https://www.irs.gov/pub/irs-pdf/fw9.pdf
2. Complete and sign the form
3. Log in to your vendor portal at <%= vendor_root_path %>
4. Navigate to "Profile" and upload your new W9 form

<%= render 'shared/mailers/status_box.text', status: :info, title: "Payment Status" do %>
Any pending payments will be held until your new W9 form is received and approved. Once approved, all held payments will be processed according to our standard payment schedule.
<% end %>

If you have already submitted an updated W9 form, please disregard this message.

If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our vendor support team immediately.

<%= render 'shared/mailers/footer.text' %>
